{"tid":1565133,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"（集思廣益）去英國告鳩陶輝","createTime":"2019-09-13T04:43:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T05:05:35.000Z","uid":258680,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f894fc3123cba5a40b7f71938fe761e9d0d33a19","tid":1565133,"uid":258680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T04:43:09.000Z","msg":"有冇神人巴絲打可以諗諗？<br />\n<br />\n原文link<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/osreadhistory/photos/a.299410663590132/1075101939354330/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fosreadhistory%2Fphotos%2Fa.299410663590132%2F1075101939354330%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4QZE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=18a5dda2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/osreadhistory/photos/a.299410663590132/1075101939354330/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n基本上都整理在圖片中<br />\n最重要要留意的是，政治庇護是依據難民公約來申請，而酷刑聲請即是依據酷刑公約<br />\n#歡迎任何形式廣傳_修正_改編_二創_不用徵求我的同意<br />\n當日直播：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/osreadhistory/videos/929458114068940/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fosreadhistory%2Fvideos%2F929458114068940%2F&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4QZE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=fb5c3592\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/osreadhistory/videos/929458114068940/</a><br />\n<br />\n政治庇護是需要由聲請人證明自己將會受到政治迫害方能申請，所以該國審查部門比較容易駁斥要求<br />\n而酷刑聲請只要有理由相信香港存在大規模侵害人權的情況，就可以提出，而且締約國不能遣返、引渡申請人<br />\n我自己本身未處理過真正的酷刑聲請，不過香港有一位酷刑聲請專家，張超雄議員，大家不妨去請教他<br />\n<br />\n酷刑公約主要是用來反制警犬的武力<br />\n在香港，違反酷刑法可處以包括終身監禁在內的任何刑期，而只有公訴程序可提起訴訟，所以&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n所以幾位英籍警司可能是有效突破口，特別是中信事件<br />\n而且酷刑定義不限於公職人員親自執行<br />\n教唆、默許都算，所以何君堯及八鄉指揮官於元朗黑夜事件值得研究<br />\n<br />\n由於香港起訴不可能，而海牙國際刑事庭並無管轄權<br />\n所以可依第五條B跟C，從外國加害者或外國受害人著手<br />\n加害者之母國有管轄權，這只要有原告就好處理<br />\n受害人之母國，其管轄權需得到該國承認方有效，連開啟起訴程序也可能有變數<br />\n反正找尋原告很重要<br />\n#希望前綫能自行組織並尋求專業協助<br />\n#我始終是學人權哲學_我不會訴訟<br />\n<br />\n另外就是著名的紐倫堡原則是適用於此公約<br />\n所以執行命令不能作為辯護理由<br />\n<br />\n最後就是此公約規範對像為公職人員及執行公權力者<br />\n一般市民並不會成為被告，除非你在執行公職人員的命令或默許<br />\n<br />\n#不要告訴我你有參與任何行動<br />\n#我不是律師_無法協助你進行起訴<br />\n#612基金看來不足以應付本地辯護需求_反制起訴可能需要另外籌款<br />\n#我們需要原告<br />\n#hooky<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ShfAb4g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FShfAb4g.jpg&h=f66cb05b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"926ed70bd278b907f6205462734f5ac0ab25119a","tid":1565133,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T04:43:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"a7d8bdbe1f0d0b063f14bbff10da38dbf43776be","tid":1565133,"uid":50979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T04:44:26.000Z","msg":"幫手推 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"409869a083eb9ffc8e19a2e09c2a8ffe5dcdf09c","tid":1565133,"uid":281342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T04:46:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://